### List all PayPal payments (default: 20 most recent)
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments

### List PayPal payments filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments?status=COMPLETED

### List PayPal payments filtered by payment type
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments?payment_type=capture

### List PayPal payments filtered by currency
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments?currency=EUR

### List PayPal payments filtered by card brand
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments?card_brand=visa

### List PayPal payments with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments?status=COMPLETED&currency=EUR&limit=5

### List PayPal payments with pagination (page 2)
GET http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments?limit=10&offset=10

### Simulate PayPal payments (from recent internal payments)
POST http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

### Simulate orphan PayPal payments (no matching internal payment)
### These produce `missing_internal` after reconciliation runs
POST http://localhost:8000/paypal-payments/simulate-orphan?count=3
Content-Type: application/json
